## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or recent changes in the job market. Additionally, the impact of internships can vary significantly across different industries and geographic locations. Further research, including interviews with employers and recent graduates, could provide more comprehensive insights into the role of internships in career development.

